snippet.title: Spirit City: Lofi Sessions - Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
We are very excited to announce that Spirit City: Lofi Sessions will be releasing on April 8th, 2024 on PC via Steam!

Spirit City: Lofi Sessions is a gamified focus tool, set to a soothing lofi soundtrack.
Discover and collect Spirits, customize your cozy virtual space, and facilitate your real-life tasks with a collection of handy features designed to improve concentration and ease stress.

Play the free demo and Wishlist us now on Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2113850/?utm_source=Reddit&utm_campaign=Youtube&utm_content=Overview

Join our growing community of Spiritographers on Discord! 
https://discord.gg/Sm8nnvnsXa

Instagram : https://instagram.com/spiritcitylofi
Tiktok : https://tiktok.com/@spiritcitylofi
Twitter : https://twitter.com/SpiritCityLofi
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/wearemooncube

Music: Coffee Hours - Gyûki
Label: Homework Radio
